node.text: Why did I feel like a drone?😢

Into the fire. 🔥 The Reykjanes Peninsula in Iceland has gone almost 800 years without any major volcanic activity. Now, for the second year in a row, hot magma is rising from craters in Meradalir valley. Head to Stories to see more. 🌋
cc: @p_shep1
